1. redesign the pages styly: Follow minimalistic style inspired by Apple’s product pages. Use plenty of whitespace, simple typography, and subtle animations. Each page should have a clear visual hierarchy, intuitive navigation, and responsive design for desktop and mobile. The Home page highlights key sections with large, striking visuals. Portfolio pages display projects in a clean grid with hover effects. Blog pages include a home listing of posts with categories, and individual post pages render content elegantly, supporting markdown. Maintain consistent styling, subtle color palette, and fast performance. Include reusable components for headers, footers, buttons, and cards to ensure scalability.
